title: Beginning Sewing: Neckwarmer
text:
Beginning Sewing: Neckwarmer
Join Lalia at Campbell County Public Library on Friday, December 6, 10am-12pm for a beginning sewing class. Learn the basics of using a sewing machine while you make a soothing, rice-filled neck warmer! All supplies provided. Class size limited to eight. Sign up today!
